{
  "text": "In this regard, researchers emphasizes the importance of gathering interpretable and actionable insights from learners who are the main users and subject of interactions with GenAI in learning to develop a thorough understanding of the circumstances in which the use of such systems may be appropriate, how students relate to GenAI, and what challenges arise during GenAI-assisted writing tasks (Rosé et al., 2019; Zawacki-Richter et al., 2019)."
}